Lectures are given on selected topics, and students are expected to write a reaction paper on each lecture. Reaction papers are to be submitted on SFC-SFS. Each student decides on his or her research topic closely related to the course, and write their term paper. It's about 10 pages (A4 paper, roughly 10,000 letters）.

